org.seedstack.business.assembler.dsl

Interface AssemblePage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AssembleMultiple
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AssemblePageWithQualifier

    public interface AssemblePage
extends AssembleMultiple
    An element of the FluentAssembler DSL allowing to assemble to a Page of multiple DTO. This is only available in the DSL if a page of aggregates has been specified as input.
